::Prowl::

Prowl looks at Bluestreak and Ratchet.

"Fall back?" he says, a bit shocked, rolling away from Gigatron's 
fire and firing a shot at Defecion, "Sorry, brother, falling back is 
not an option. If they get the Ark, we'll be dead in a few seconds 
from time disruption!"
